---
// Mission Statement Section - Why accessibility is our advantage
---

<section class="mission">
  <div class="mission-content">
    <h2>Your Advantage: Accessible by Design</h2>
    <div class="mission-text">
      <p>
        Our identity isn't just a feature; it's our greatest strength. As members of the Deaf community,
        we live and breathe accessibility. We understand firsthand the barriers that non-inclusive design
        can create, and more importantly, we see the incredible opportunity that accessible technology
        offers to connect people.
      </p>
      <p>
        This unique perspective is embedded in every line of code we write, every solution we architect,
        and every project we deliver. We don't add accessibility as an afterthought; we build it from the core.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 120px 20px;
    background: rgb(var(--gray-light));
  }

  .mission-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mission h2 {
    font-size: 2.441em;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 0 0 40px 0;
    color: rgb(var(--black));
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .mission-text {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .mission-text p {
    font-size: 1.25em;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
  }

  .mission-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Mobile responsive */
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .mission {
      padding: 80px 16px;
    }

    .mission-content {
      padding: 0 8px;
    }

    .mission h2 {
      font-size: 1.953em;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .mission-text {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .mission-text p {
      font-size: 1.05em;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
  }

  /* Dark mode */
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .mission {
      background: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
    }

    .mission h2 {
      color: rgb(var(--gray-light));
    }

    .mission-text p {
      color: rgb(var(--gray));
    }
  }
</style>
